{"tid":1397420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"說話要說清楚，港獨是由港共炮製的一場戲碼","createTime":"2019-08-02T12:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T00:54:24.000Z","uid":110123,"like":96,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"20ba6e3e6e146cf965fc2f2d59f3d18cd81edca2","tid":1397420,"uid":110123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:51:52.000Z","msg":"說話要說清楚，港獨是由港共炮製的一場戲碼<br />\n由始至終港獨都不曾存在<br />\n直至梁振英高舉民族論開始<br />\n目的就是令政府定性香港分裂勢力攪局<br />\n來阻礙香港原本基本法所付予的高度自治進程<br />\n從而令香港民主發展原地踏步<br />\n遲遲都未有雙普選的最主要原因<br />\n<br />\n香港人不要再被政府帶風向！<br />\n雙普選民主進程不是中國施捨的<br />\n而是基本法，一國兩制所付予的權利<br />\n<br />\n香港人祇是取回應得的權利！不要再被騙了！"},{"pid":"ee974014ff4ec69a5359b1dc708fdeb29fa94d72","tid":1397420,"uid":110123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:08:05.000Z","msg":"推!!"},{"pid":"2817b313fa560d902ec3f4208ab838e2ca9c7318","tid":1397420,"uid":110123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:13:39.000Z","msg":"推!!"},{"pid":"69bbb9c96f8fde87d9057de98e49ec1af9c7613b","tid":1397420,"uid":58883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee974014ff4ec69a5359b1dc708fdeb29fa94d72","tid":1397420,"uid":110123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:08:05.000Z","msg":"推!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:32:57.000Z","msg":"[參考波蘭成功例子既最佳戰術] 完全剋制政府冷處理 - 罷買 <br />\n一個最有效既長期戰術, 麻煩入去睇睇<br />\n<br />\n1. 週期性罷買係相當可行既一個戰術, 因為更能夠令普通人適應<br />\n2. 罷買影響力可以好大<br />\n3. 政府用冷處理戰術,打算拖至9月,而罷買係開學之後一樣可以實行,可以向社會施加壓力既最好方法<br />\n4. 罷買比遊行, 三罷, 更能夠說服中立派/和理非行動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1397444/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1397444/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"84af9dd01b18caecd6abfd1156a89528b59e2152","tid":1397420,"uid":224479,"like":6,"dislike":19,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:39:35.000Z","msg":"唔知你真心定假膠<br />\n係到反港獨會被人咬死<br />\n雖然我真係反對香港獨立 只係支持一國兩制下雙普選<br />\n但唔敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a29b9be8727e5b982d60bcd7d1b5f1c437cf825","tid":1397420,"uid":110123,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"84af9dd01b18caecd6abfd1156a89528b59e2152","tid":1397420,"uid":224479,"like":6,"dislike":19,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:39:35.000Z","msg":"唔知你真心定假膠<br />\n係到反港獨會被人咬死<br />\n雖然我真係反對香港獨立 只係支持一國兩制下雙普選<br />\n但唔敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:44:04.000Z","msg":"我知會比人屌, 但再係咁, 香港人實會攬住一齊死架啦, 到時再互屌都無地方啦"},{"pid":"10224762ae5f7fcd53dafcba809bcde4328459bf","tid":1397420,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:45:51.000Z","msg":"基本法係0708 雙普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7d01a7aef8f98094d10effde0a322f12652ab1","tid":1397420,"uid":296640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:46:09.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 點解要罷工 瘋傳比d唔知罷黎做咩既人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1397455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1397455</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n瘋傳d唔知罷黎做咩 唔想罷 唔知點罷 既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a8ccebc63c8ef4f2b224ecfa2257475bf88d3e","tid":1397420,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390913</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有興趣請入Group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=793b5b40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA</a>"},{"pid":"140d0406f77c99e442b08284293fe975158df5b0","tid":1397420,"uid":34334,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆